QuestData.Title: We'll Poke Their Eye Out
QuestData.Description: The Javelins were some of Suramar's finest creations before the Sundering. Their magic is ancient and potent. Perhaps strong enough to defeat Azshara's wards.$b$bHurry back to Newhome. We must tell the others of our success here. You have done well.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return to Lor'themar Theron in Newhome.
